     1	# A Tao Screen Can Be Operational On An Exact-But-Noncoercive Ledger If It Is Only Used As An Admission Filter
     2	
     3	When a branch has not yet earned a coercive invariant package, Tao sensitivity
     4	can still become operational, but only in a narrower role.
